{"tid":2237351,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BBC直播雙十國慶大典稱「北韓建國75週年」　","createTime":"2020-10-10T07:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T10:05:51.000Z","uid":37554,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce0a6086682eed7fc32164a374d6fde6057ffaf","tid":2237351,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:32:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201010/1828499.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20201010%2F1828499.htm&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDFtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=3089964c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201010/1828499.htm</a><br />\n記者王佩翊／編譯<br />\n<br />\n雙十國慶大會10日於總統府前廣場盛大舉行，國防部三軍聯合樂儀隊更是祭出精彩表演，吸引各家外媒關注。然而英國廣播公司新聞頻道（BBC）在直播我國國慶大典時，明明整個畫面都佈滿青天白日滿地紅的旗幟，卻將標題誤植為「北韓舉辦建國75周年大典」，直播地點更是直接打上大大的「平壤」，讓亞洲網友看了實在是很傻眼。據網友稱，稍早BBC已經更在相關畫面並對此做出道歉聲明。<br />\n<br />\n日本網友須藤玲司稍早在推特上發文表示，「BBC說這是『北韓舉辦建國75周年大典』，並同步於平壤進行直播...但這個畫面錯了吧？」並附上4張照片。從該名網友所翻攝的畫面中可以看到，BBC竟在國防部三軍聯合樂儀隊進行表演時，於畫面左上角的直播地點寫上「平壤」，實在是太過荒唐。網友透露，BBC直到30分鐘後才發現錯誤，進行更正並道歉<br />\n<br />\n根據另一名網友拍攝的影片中更可以聽到，主播看著我國國慶大典三軍聯合樂儀隊的表演時，直稱「這是在平壤」，讓觀眾看到超傻眼。事實上，在直播畫面中不斷出現台灣青天白日滿地紅的旗幟，連網友們看了都直搖頭表示，「這怎麼看都是台灣國慶日吧」、「除了BBC以外大家都知道（是台灣）」、「BBC太誇張了」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ej7keQrVcAEAPsQ?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEj7keQrVcAEAPsQ%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=8b0372e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ej7kemxVgAAzt8g?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEj7kemxVgAAzt8g%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=8dc4f97a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/john.harlow3/videos/10158727437776280/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjohn.harlow3%2Fvideos%2F10158727437776280%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDFtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=7e7c947b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/john.harlow3/videos/10158727437776280/</a>"},{"pid":"b45a2043b96ea907639069455e4a59e40760a3b9","tid":2237351,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:34:55.000Z","msg":"台灣萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db949ef1746957366825bb227cd42059f1d75117","tid":2237351,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:35:59.000Z","msg":"英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e27769956b417f073b9c7af32aa1c19131e2e9","tid":2237351,"uid":43173,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T07:50:53.000Z","msg":"BBC<img src=\"https://www.novinite.com/media/images/2018-01/photo_verybig_186659.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.novinite.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2018-01%2Fphoto_verybig_186659.jpg&h=db8a98aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20064bd318eda6429878e57373acc69fb6117db2","tid":2237351,"uid":344679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T08:08:31.000Z","msg":"懷疑根本有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a75d6dc524cffffb5bf1e9b0e86ebbb94b69559","tid":2237351,"uid":56624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"其實10月10 係勞動黨75周年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f1f694ac021b572f204d60f47705d77d7620bc","tid":2237351,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"20064bd318eda6429878e57373acc69fb6117db2","tid":2237351,"uid":344679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T08:08:31.000Z","msg":"懷疑根本有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T08:23:36.000Z","msg":"BBC中文網 快D遷移返香港（中國境內）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /